Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:40.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My eternal liege, the ultimate demon who\nknows no rival...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.05,0:01:42.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}my Lord Sesshomaru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:46.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}His father's heirloom, Tetsusaiga,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:50.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}known to fell a hundred demons\nin one sweep...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.53,0:01:53.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And only my Lord Sesshomaru is\nworthy of its magnificence!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:58.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such a sword is wasted on\NLord Sesshomaru's younger brother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:02.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha, that despicable half-demon\nwith a mortal for a mother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:28.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:30.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, Lord Sesshomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.97,0:02:34.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When you're hungry,\nyou must find your own food.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:36.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right! I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:46.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru instructed Rin to\nfind her own food.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then he tells me to go\nhelp her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Jaken, how far\nmust we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:55.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How far?! Until we find food!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:59.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Jaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:03.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just how are you of\nservice to Lord Sesshomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:04.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Whaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:06.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I serve him in many ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:08.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Many ways?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:10.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For instance...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:17.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha's Tetsusaiga\nturned bright red.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:22.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't fathom\nhow Lord Sesshomaru feels.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:27.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Inuyasha's sword can even\nbreak through a demon barrier.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:30.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's become extremely dangerous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:34.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, Lord Sesshomaru has\nhis sword Tokijin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As well as Tenseiga...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But no good can come out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}of Inuyasha wielding such\na frightening sword.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:44.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it! Just prevent\nhim from holding the sword!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:47.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:49.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Today, you shall witness...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:55.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,how I serve my Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:58.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, next! Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:03:59.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:01.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:03.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! We win again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:08.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure feels good to win\nover and over again. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:09.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:13.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:16.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, can you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:19.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:25.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, can you stop sighing\nso much? It's irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:28.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you hadn't shown the same\nhand as me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we'd have had another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:32.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:36.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, you really wanted to\nstay back with me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:40.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen! l just lost, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or... is this hand cursed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:47.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's your personality\nthat's cursed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:52.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We did it!\NWe've won again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We won with paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So that's Wind Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:58.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wi-nd Tun-nel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:01.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Sure you aren't cheating?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:03.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop being a sore loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:04.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:09.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here they come! At last!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:11.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop dawdling!\NThey're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Appear, No-Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:19.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You summoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:22.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No-Man, Inuyasha and his\ngroup are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:25.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get close to them and\nsteal Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:28.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are a demon borne out\nof the regrets of Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:30.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should be able to\ngrasp Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:32.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now go and steal it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:37.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The one that Inuyasha\ntreasures so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:38.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it valuable?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, so go and get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We did it!\NWe won again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, you're so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:50.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yup, I'm really good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, scissors is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:55.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hi-rai-ko-tsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:58.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez, I can't see Kagome anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we can't see them,\nwe won't know if they cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:03.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:05.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, something's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:08.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:11.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:14.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A mist?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:16.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,More like smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:19.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A mountain fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, it's not fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:26.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It wasn't me who did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:30.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone's pulling at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:31.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:32.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:38.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:39.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel shards are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:41.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... he's late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:47.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:50.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The treasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! Did you get Tetsusaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:56.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:59.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These aren't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:01.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:05.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mmm... treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:08.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:10.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no need of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You didn't get Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:20.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He had an old, rusty sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:26.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It sure didn't look like a treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:28.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:29.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, go and get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:33.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's so slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Jaken, are you sure\nthat demon can handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:41.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How I wish I had\nmy henchmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember those days...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:46.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I was the commander\nof many.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back then, I led hundreds\nof demons{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:53.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and controlled the\nplains of Musashi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:56.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that time, we were at battle\nwith demons{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:59.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}who controlled the\neastern mountains.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:03.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their leader was Bikuni, who,\ndespite being several hundred years old,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:05.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}was a formidable foe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:11.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just then!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're in my way!\NMove.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:20.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:24.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I said you're in the way.\NDo you not understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:34.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Clear... clear the path!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:49.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How beautiful...\NHe's so dashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:55.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:57.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive my rudeness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:03.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It may not have been\nyour intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but you have saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:09.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I beg you! I beg you!\NMake me your servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:17.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A moment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:30.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:36.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um... What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:39.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you can use it,\NI'll entrust it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:43.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please tell me your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:50.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:53.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:55.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:58.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Several decades have\npassed since that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:10:01.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I have long sought\nto repay my debt to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:06.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I cannot leave this\nto No-Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Jaken is so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:17.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the robber?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:23.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Turn over the Sacred Jewel\nshards or you'll be sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:26.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have some nerve,\nstealing things from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:30.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... a sword... a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:31.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:33.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:36.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:42.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! You bounced right off\NTetsusaiga's barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:45.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what happens when\na demon tries to touch Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:50.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In this age of wars, men have\nlost lands and farms...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lost homes to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:55.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The amassed regret and bitterness\nof such men
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:58.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,gave rise to this demon\NNo-Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:02.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... I sorta feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:06.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look, if he returns everything,\nlet's let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There're the shards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- My top!\N- My things, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't do anything bad now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:24.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you do,\NWe'll have to destroy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:28.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you'd like, I'll recite\na sutra for your spirits' repose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:30.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was pretty earnest\nabout this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Strange demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, there are all kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:39.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! That hopeless demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:40.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:42.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hot! I'm burning!\NHot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Water! Where's water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:50.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Water! Water! Water! Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:51.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:11:59.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you hear a\nweird voice just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:02.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:04.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Probably your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:06.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've taken care of\nthe demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:07.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,let's move on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:08.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:14.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:16.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does it hurt, Master Jaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:18.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:20.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Then will you give up?\N- I will NOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:22.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Move away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:24.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin, just go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:27.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You said you wanted me\nto watch you in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:29.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just wait, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.61,0:12:37.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I SHALL take Tetsusaiga\naway from you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:41.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Man! We sure wasted\ntime back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:44.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello there... travelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:51.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"In training. Will examine\nyour lives and sharpen for free."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:54.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I dunno what that means,\nbut something smells weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:58.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is good for\nbuilding character.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:03.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Inuyasha... This incense\nhas dulled his sense of smell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he doesn't recognize\nthat I'm Jaken!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:09.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you desire, I will sharpen\nyour lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:11.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:13.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He means your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:15.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:17.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yes... yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:21.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... Unusual to find\na sword sharpener.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:24.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're a craftsman of\nthe feudal age.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:26.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll take you\nup on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:28.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's free, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:31.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Free? That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please do a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're a generous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:38.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So that's about it.\NWe'll stop by later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:39.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Counting on ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:43.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! That Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:44.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right! I'll sharpen them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:47.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If these weapons are\nsuper sharp,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:51.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha will want me to\nsharpen Tetsusaiga, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:54.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And... that will be\nthe perfect opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:56.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sharpen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:00.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sharpen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:01.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go for it, Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:03.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go for it, Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:04.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone, together now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're in my way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:16.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Humph! Who cares\nabout Master Jaken!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:18.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:23.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought of something!\NCome, Aun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:26.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow! So shiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:29.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is fine work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:32.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:35.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shucks! I shoulda left\nmy sword, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:38.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this old man is fast\nasleep from exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:40.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's not wake him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:43.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's just leave him\na thank-you note.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:45.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh well... too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:51.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Thank you very much."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:57.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:02.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gone!\NAll gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:06.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They've left!\NI've been duped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:08.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sharpened those weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:10.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to trick Inuyasha\nand steal his sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I've lost my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:16.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh yes... I still have\nthat option.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just watch, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:37.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On this night, you and Tetsusaiga\nshall be separated!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:55.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that I've gathered flowers\nfor Lord Sesshomaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:56.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we have to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:05.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... How did we\nget back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:07.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:09.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know which way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:12.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, do you smell Lord Sesshomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:17.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see... Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go to Master Jaken then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We sure walked a lot today...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:29.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:30.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:32.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that... a hot spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:34.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:37.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow! Looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such luck, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we bathe together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess we'll go separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:46.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:50.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}While Inuyasha is\nin the spring,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:53.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shall steal away\nhis Tetsusaiga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:55.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a nice bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:17:01.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha isn't around.\NDo dog-demons hate baths?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:03.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shoulda asked, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:05.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're talking about\nthat sharpener?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:08.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... He looked pretty skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:11.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sharpener?\NShould I appear as a sharpener?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:14.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I can take Tetsusaiga!\NAll right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:16.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, we're done here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:18.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Yeah!\N- Shall we go then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:21.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! He's gonna bathe?\NMake up your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:26.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't peek!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:29.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who'd peek at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:32.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, he didn't mean me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:34.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nice bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:35.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay in there for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:45.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:47.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Found Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:54.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My bad! Wrong move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:55.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:17:59.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Use this to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did it! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:09.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:12.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everything's spinning...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:16.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Same here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:18.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:23.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-Sessho... maru is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll try to stall him.\NDo something about these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:27.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But do what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:34.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Over there... my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There! I found their clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But where's Tetsusaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:41.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Jaken, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Rin?\NWhy are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:47.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:50.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no!\NNo, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:52.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin is human, she can\nhold Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:55.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin, take this and\ngo to Lord Sesshomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:56.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:00.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:06.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin, go while I hold her off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go around him, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:18.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:25.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it, Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Return my Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:33.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I dunno what you're\ntalking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:34.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:38.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:41.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin, you fool!\NWhy did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:44.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:46.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:48.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A girl?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:50.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grab on, Master Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:51.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:53.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang on tight, Master Jaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:01.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin, why did you return?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:05.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:11.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yes, where is Tetsusaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:12.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:14.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:15.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.37,0:20:17.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:26.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What's the matter,\NMaster Jaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:27.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:29.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:32.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn that Jaken!\NI'll get 'im next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:35.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga seems to be\nwhat he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:38.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru himself was\nnowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:41.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jaken worked alone on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:43.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was something stolen from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:51.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one's noticed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:55.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sesshomaru is supposed to\ndespise humans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:57.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet it was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:21:01.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a human girl\nwho saved Jaken.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:04.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's the meaning of this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:10.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}All that work for nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:12.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They all look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:15.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which would you choose,\NMaster Jaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:16.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whichever! I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:19.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll take two,\neven three.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:22.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lord Sesshomaru\nand his whims!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:24.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keeping a human girl\nat his side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:27.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is so sweet, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:30.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Jaken, you keep\nwatch okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:33.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh well, it cannot be helped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:36.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was worried about you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:40.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That moment, if Rin had\nnot returned,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:44.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I would have been beaten\nbadly by Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:50.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! You're!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:53.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru can be\nso careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Taking his eyes off\nhis ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:01.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:02.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.14,0:22:04.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:07.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Riiiin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:51.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!\NRin has been abducted!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.55,0:23:52.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:55.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's he up to anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.39,0:23:58.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool! Did he think that I would\ntake action
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.82,0:24:00.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,over a mere mortal?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:03.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And yet, he still walked straight\ninto Naraku's den!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.73,0:24:07.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!\NTalk about shy and reserved!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.37,0:24:11.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Sesshomaru and the Abducted Rin"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.90,0:24:14.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait! Lord Sesshomaru!
